(firstQuint)Effectiveness of Virtual Reality Exercises in STroke Rehabilitation (EVREST).

 A pilot, randomized (1:1) controlled trial to compare the safety and feasibility of Nintendo Wii gaming versus other recreational therapy activities (playing cards) in post-stroke patients.

 All patients will continue to receive all other standard medical and physiotherapy treatments while in the study.

